    "nodes": [
      {
        "id": "comment-1",
        "type": "nodetool.workflows.base_node.Comment",
        "data": {
          "comment": "# 🎬 AI Product Launch Video Generator\n\nTurn a campaign brief and product image into a cinematic launch clip. A prompt node combines your inputs, an agent writes an image-to-video prompt, then an Image-to-Video model animates the product shot.\n\n**Pipeline:** Brief + Audience + Features + Image → Build prompt → Write video prompt (agent) → Animate video\n\n**Try this:** choose a language model and video model, then swap the product image or rewrite the agent's system prompt for a different tone.\n\n**Cost note:** the animation step runs on Veo 3.1, a paid per-second video model — each run costs noticeably more than an image-only template."
        },
        "ui_properties": {
          "position": {
            "x": -460,
            "y": -247
          },
          "zIndex": 0,
          "width": 437,
          "height": 340,
          "selectable": true,
          "bypassed": false
        },
        "dynamic_properties": {},
        "dynamic_outputs": {}
      },
      {
        "id": "4",
        "type": "nodetool.text.Prompt",
        "data": {
          "prompt": "Using the text and image inputs, write a video prompt for a single 16:9 product shot. Give clear instructions on the animations and movements in the video.\n\nRules:\n- Present tense, visually concrete; one clear camera move and one primary subject action.\n- Include: subject, setting, time-of-day, camera language (framing, angle, lens, movement), composition cues, lighting, 3–5 color anchors, atmosphere/texture, and realistic motion cues.\n- Emphasize the product and key features naturally within the scene for the target audience and tone.\n- Finish with constraints: no on-screen text, no logos, no watermarks, no glitches, no distorted anatomy.\n\nInputs:\n- Campaign brief: {{ brief }}\n- Target audience: {{ audience }}\n- Key features: {{ features }}"
        },
        "ui_properties": {
          "selected": false,
          "position": {
            "x": 390,
            "y": -7
          },
          "zIndex": 0,
          "width": 486,
          "height": 567,
          "title": "5️⃣ Build prompt",
          "selectable": true,
          "bypassed": false
        },
        "dynamic_properties": {
          "brief": "Launch video for the Aurora Trail smart fitness watch, highlighting outdoor adventure tracking.",
          "audience": "active millennials who enjoy weekend hiking and fitness challenges",
          "features": "GPS navigation, heart-rate analytics, adaptive coaching, water resistance"
        },
        "dynamic_outputs": {}
      },
      {
        "id": "3",
        "type": "nodetool.agents.Agent",
        "data": {
          "model": {
            "type": "language_model",
            "provider": "openai",
            "id": "gpt-5-mini",
            "name": "GPT-5 mini",
            "path": null,
            "supported_tasks": []
          },
          "system": "You are a prompt engineer specializing in image-to-video generation models.\n\nTask: read the campaign brief, target audience, and key features, then rewrite them as a single production-ready image-to-video prompt for the attached product photo.\n\nOutput format: plain text, one paragraph, no markdown, no headers, no lists, no preamble. Return only the finished prompt.",
